<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Peculiar Lads Guild | Dragon Nest SEA</title>
	<link href="/css/app.css" rel="stylesheet">
	@vite('resources/css/app.css')
	<meta name="description" content="Peculiar Lads is a Dragon Nest SEA guild for unique adventurers and friends. Join us in Lagendia!">
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-900 via-purple-900 to-indigo-700 min-h-screen flex flex-col">
	<header class="py-8 bg-indigo-950 shadow-lg">
		<div class="container mx-auto flex flex-col items-center">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-yellow-300 tracking-wide drop-shadow-lg flex items-center gap-3">
				<img src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/dragonnest/images/7/7e/Dragon_Nest_Logo.png" alt="Dragon Nest SEA Logo" class="h-12 md:h-16 inline-block align-middle"> Peculiar Lads
			</h1>
			<p class="mt-2 text-lg md:text-2xl text-indigo-200 font-medium">Dragon Nest SEA Guild of Uniqueness & Brotherhood</p>
			<span class="mt-1 text-sm text-indigo-300">Server: <span class="font-semibold">Lagendia</span></span>
		</div>
	</header>
	<main class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-4">
		<section class="bg-white/80 rounded-xl shadow-xl p-8 max-w-2xl w-full mt-10">
			<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-900 mb-4">Welcome, Dragon Nest SEA Adventurer!</h2>
			<p class="text-indigo-800 mb-6">Peculiar Lads is a Dragon Nest SEA guild based on the <span class="font-semibold text-yellow-700">Lagendia</span> server. We are a brotherhood of dreamers, doers, and those who dare to be different. Whether you’re a PvE enthusiast, PvP challenger, or just here for the fun and friendship, you belong here!</p>
			<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-indigo-700 space-y-2">
				<li>🐉 Run nests, raids, and dungeons together</li>
				<li>⚔️ Guild PvP and GvG events</li>
				<li>🎉 Weekly Dragon Nest SEA activities</li>
				<li>🤝 Forge lifelong friendships in Lagendia</li>
				<li>🏆 Celebrate our unique achievements</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
				<a href="#join" class="bg-yellow-500 hover:bg-yellow-600 text-indigo-900 font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg shadow transition">Join the Guild</a>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section id="join" class="mt-16 max-w-xl w-full">
			<form class="bg-white/90 rounded-lg shadow p-6 flex flex-col gap-4">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-900 mb-2">Apply to Peculiar Lads (Dragon Nest SEA)</h3>
				<input type="text" placeholder="Character Name" class="px-4 py-2 rounded border border-yellow-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-400 outline-none" required>
				<input type="text" placeholder="Class (e.g. Warrior, Sorceress)" class="px-4 py-2 rounded border border-yellow-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-400 outline-none" required>
				<input type="email" placeholder="Contact Email" class="px-4 py-2 rounded border border-yellow-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-400 outline-none" required>
				<textarea placeholder="Why do you want to join our Dragon Nest SEA guild?" class="px-4 py-2 rounded border border-yellow-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-400 outline-none" rows="3" required></textarea>
				<button type="submit" class="bg-yellow-500 hover:bg-yellow-600 text-indigo-900 font-bold py-2 rounded transition">Apply Now</button>
			</form>
		</section>
	</main>
	<footer class="py-6 bg-indigo-950 text-center text-indigo-200 mt-12">
		<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
			<span>&copy; 2026 Peculiar Lads Guild — Dragon Nest SEA, Lagendia Server.</span>
			<span class="text-xs text-indigo-400">Not affiliated with Eyedentity Games or PlayPark. For fans, by fans.</span>
		</div>
	</footer>
</body>
</html>
